  </div>
</section>

<!-- TRUST STRIP -->
<div class="trust">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="trust-item"><span class="dot"></span>Open 7 days, 9:30am–10pm</div>
    <div class="trust-item"><span class="dot"></span>Same-day & last-minute cuts</div>
    <div class="trust-item"><span class="dot"></span>20+ years of repeat clients</div>
    <div class="trust-item"><span class="dot"></span>Men, women & kids welcome</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SERVICES -->
<section id="services">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">Services</div>
      <h2>Precision cuts, honest pricing.</h2>
      <p>No hidden fees, no pressure to add services you didn't ask for. Just tell us what you want — we'll get it right.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <h3>Men's Haircut</h3>
        <p>Classic, fade, or modern styles — tailored to your face shape and how you actually wear your hair day to day.</p>
        <div class="service-meta"><span>~30 min</span><span class="price">$20</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <h3>Women's Haircut</h3>
        <p>From a simple trim to a full style change, with layers and shaping built to be easy to maintain at home.</p>
        <div class="service-meta"><span>~45 min</span><span class="price">$30+</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
