        <div class="service-meta"><span>~15 min</span><span class="price">$12</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <h3>Color, Perm &amp; Foil</h3>
        <p>Full color, partial foils, or a perm — done with care and a clear sense of what will actually suit you.</p>
        <div class="service-meta"><span>~60–90 min</span><span class="price">$60+</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <h3>Kids' Haircut</h3>
        <p>Patient, quick, and painless — even for the squirmy ones. A go-to for Olympia families.</p>
        <div class="service-meta"><span>~20 min</span><span class="price">$15</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <h3>Wedding &amp; Event Styling</h3>
        <p>Special-occasion styling designed to hold up for photos and last through the whole event.</p>
        <div class="service-meta"><span>By appointment</span><span class="price">$50+</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY US -->
<section id="why" class="why-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--copper-light)">Why Olympia Chooses Tony's</div>
      <h2>Twenty years of getting it right.</h2>
      <p>There's a reason clients have been coming back for decades — and why their kids come here now too.</p>
