      <p style="margin-top:18px;color:#5a5448;max-width:55ch;">Tony has been cutting hair in Olympia for over two decades, building a client list that includes families who've trusted him for three haircuts in a row — kid, parent, and grandparent. Wendy brings the same eye for detail to color, styling, and women's cuts, helping clients find a look that actually fits their life.</p>
